high_descs: Turn around, move to the left over to the sink in the corner.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Turn right, bring the potato to the fridge.
Chill the potato in the fridge.
Bring the potato left, to the counter right of the sink.
Put the chilled potato on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato on the counter in front of the coffee machine.

high_descs: Pick up the potato that is on the counter in front of the sink.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge for a couple seconds to get cold then take it out.
Turn left and walk over to where the coffee machine is on the counter.
Put the potato on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right for three steps, turn right for four steps, turn left for four steps, turn right and stop in front of the counter.
Pick up the potato from the counter that’s to the left of the potato.
Turn right for four steps, turn left to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and put the potato near the front left of the second shelf, shut the door and wait for a few seconds, open the door and take out the potato then shut the door again.
Turn left and walk three steps, turn right to face the counter.
Put the potato on the counter, in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a potato on the counter, in front of the coffee machine.
